main event: A military observation reported a bright possible satellite on 14 Jan 62, estimated to be at a very high altitude.
interesting points: The object was described as very luminous and appeared to be in constant motion,Estimated altitude was between 20,000 to 30,000 feet,The observation was linked to an Echo satellite pass during the same timeframe,There were multiple possible explanations for the sighting such as a balloon, aircraft, or astronomical object,The coordinates of the sighting were 31-39N 171-52E.
